OL,7,FA jury in the case of a cyclist
OL,8,Faccused of causing the death of an
OL,9,Felderly pedestrian in Oxford has
OL,10,Fretired to consider its verdict.
OL,12,FPolly Friedhoff was knocked down while
OL,13,Fwalking on a footpath near Iffley Lock
OL,14,Fon 20 November 2022.
OL,16,FThe court heard Ms Friedhoff, was a
OL,17,Ffit and active woman. She was walking
OL,18,Falonsgside a friend before a bike
OL,19,Fcollided with her that the prosecution
OL,20,Fdescribed as "far faster than walking
OL,21,Fspeed".
