OL,7,FShe suffered serious injuries and was
OL,8,Ftaken to the John Radcliffe Hospital
OL,9,Fin Headington, where she died on 2
OL,10,FDecember 2022.
OL,12,FEdward Bressan, 56, was charged with
OL,13,Friding a bicycle without due care and
OL,14,Fattention and a second offence of
OL,15,F"having charge of a bicycle by wanton
OL,16,For furious driving".
OL,18,FHe denies the charges.
