OL,7,FThe university lecturer told the court
OL,8,Fhow he is an experienced cyclist,
OL,9,Friding through Oxford for 40 years,
OL,10,Fcycling down that specific towpath
OL,11,Fhundreds of times.
OL,13,FEvidence pointed out by the defence
OL,14,FKuljeet Dobe in his closing
OL,15,Fstatements, highlighted two witnesses
OL,16,Fdisputing reckless driving.
