OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe defence barrister said they
OL,8,Fcorroborate claims made by Bressan
OL,9,Fthat he slowed down when approaching
OL,10,Fto overtake and Polly simply lost her
OL,11,Fbalance.
OL,13,FThe court heard how it was too late
OL,14,Ffor him to react, and Ms Friedhoff
OL,15,Fdidn't have enough time to put her
OL,16,Fhands out to protect herself, falling
OL,17,Fonto the towpath.
