OL,7,FBressan always claims he rang his
OL,8,Fbell, and saw Ms Friedhoff move to the
OL,9,Fside. Jurors were told the he was just
OL,10,Fan "unwitting actor in tragic
OL,11,Fevents...leading to the sad demise of
OL,12,Fa good lady."
OL,14,FThe close friend, who was with her at
OL,15,Fthe time, Ewa Huggins, said Ms
OL,16,FFriedhoff was "catapulted forward into
OL,17,Fthe air during the collision."
