OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe defence argued this would have
OL,8,Fmeant Ms Friedhoff would have injuries
OL,9,Ffrom that crash and so would Bressan,
OL,10,Fbut all her injuries were related to a
OL,11,Ffall and Bressan was not injured.
OL,13,FJudge Ian Pringle told jurors that, in
OL,14,Forder to deliver a guilty verdict,
OL,15,Fthey had to be sure that the cause of
OL,16,Fthe collision was Bressan's "wilful
OL,17,Fconduct", and that is was not only
OL,18,Fdeliberate but "reckless."
OL,20,FThe jury will continue with their
OL,21,Fdeliberations on Thursday (11 July).
